    <div class="main review-item" id="1184253">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1184253/" class="title-link">先制宪后建国</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1184253"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/xwl/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1038112-6.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/xwl/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">未临</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2007-07-25"
      class="main-meta">2007-07-25 11:55:19</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1184253_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  美利坚合众国，的确非常有意思，先制宪后建国。许久前，当了解到众议院是按人口分席位，参议院则按州分时，就纳闷怎么分配得如此公平。同此类似，NBA 的制度也是相当地公平。读了易中天的这本书，才令人豁然开朗！易先生的文笔的确是很不错。 

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/1184253/#comments">(1回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">9有用 / 0没用</span>
                        <span class="publisher left">
                            山东画报出版社2004版</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_1184253_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_1184253_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





